=Description=

"Modern Poland Foundation is a non-profit working in the field of [[Open Educational Resources]] and promoting idea of free and unrestricted access to knowledge. We run programs such as "[[Free Textbooks]]" (teachers write
textbooks for schools in an open, participatory production model), "Free
Readings" (innovative internet school library with public domain books
served in a rich, inter-textual manner) and "Reading by
listening" (audio-books of obligatory school readings read by
professional actors). All software and content produced in a Foundation
programs is released under one of the free licenses."


